data.description: This beautifully maintained home offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and classic appeal. As you step inside, you're greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere, highlighted by the abundance of natural light that streams through the windows, illuminating the spacious living areas. The open layout seamlessly connects the living room, bedrooms and  kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining guests or simply relaxing with loved ones. Outside, the expansive backyard provides a serene oasis where you can unwind. The sehd offers parking for outdoor equipment  and additional storage space. Don't miss your chance to make this delightful property your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the best of Portsmouth living at 10 Byers!
